text: puokke( chin) thveukear aoy saou lai mean tam avei delke chng dauch chea vimean khpasa roubachamleak ning chan da thom dauch sreahtuk haeyning chhnang del cheab now nung kanleng . ( a l laoh ban mean bantoul tha) ao pouchopongsa da vou d. chaur puok anak anouvotd tam daoy doengkoun( champoh a l laoh) choh . haey anak del doengkoun knongchamnaom khnhom robsa yeung ku techtuoch bamphot
